  <channel>
    <title>Eternal Rhythm</title>
    <link>https://www.pbsfm.org.au/program/eternal-rhythm</link>
    <description>&lt;p&gt;Eternal Rhythm is a jazz focused program that explores the deeper side of jazz from both past and present and from all around the world.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;From Spiritual jazz to Free jazz, Afrocentric jazz to Oriental jazz, odd rarities &amp;amp; modern sounds, Eternal Rhythm takes you on a musical journey and inspires to broaden the knowledge of the many directions that jazz can take.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Email: &lt;a href="mailto:eternalrhythmpbs@gmail.com" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(204, 34, 41); text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold;" target="_blank"&gt;eternalrhythmpbs@gmail.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
